flowchart LR
  U["User Goal Fix test failure"] --> C["Core Runtime organizes a round of requests"]
  C --> P["Provider Runtime calls the real model"]
  P --> S["Streaming Adapter normalized events"]
  S --> E["ModelEvent\ntext / reasoning / finish / usage / error"]
  S --> I["ToolIntent only describes actions"]
  E --> C
  I --> C
  C --> L["Event Log records facts"]
  C --> T["Tool Pipeline Verification/Permissions/Execution"]
  T --> O["Observation result backfill"]
  O --> C

  P -. "Unable to execute tool" .-> T
  I:::hot
  C:::hot
  T:::hot

  classDef hot fill:#fff3b0,stroke:#111,stroke-width:2px,color:#111;
